          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 79917,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Programs like the one below regularly need to perform the same task over and over.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 275px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img height=180 src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/volume-icon.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;increase()&quot;&gt;Increase volume&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    let volume = 0;&#xA;    &#xA;    function increase() {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;).innerHTML =&#xA;      &quot;Volume increased!&quot;;&#xA;     const s = document.getElementById('container').style;&#xA;     s.display = &quot;block&quot;;&#xA;     s.opacity = 1;&#xA;     (function fade() {&#xA;      if ((s.opacity -= .1) &lt; 0) s.display = &quot;none&quot;;&#xA;      else setTimeout(fade, 150);&#xA;     })();&#xA;    }&#xA;   &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 79895,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Instead of rewriting the same code, we can use <strong>functions</strong> to group related code and perform the task in one place.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 275px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img height=180 src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/volume-icon.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;decrease()&quot;&gt;Decrease volume&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    let volume = 0;&#xA;    &#xA;    function decrease() {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;).innerHTML =&#xA;      &quot;Volume decreased!&quot;;&#xA;     const s = document.getElementById('container').style;&#xA;     s.display = &quot;block&quot;;&#xA;     s.opacity = 1;&#xA;     (function fade() {&#xA;      if ((s.opacity -= .1) &lt; 0) s.display = &quot;none&quot;;&#xA;      else setTimeout(fade, 150);&#xA;     })();&#xA;    }&#xA;   &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Functions",
            "id": 79921,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>To begin grouping related code, we start defining a function with the keyword <code>def</code>. </p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>def</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Functions",
            "id": 79920,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Next comes the function's name in snake case, like <code>greet_user</code>, followed by parentheses, <code>(</code> and <code>)</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_user\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>greet_user</code>, followed by <code>(</code>, and finally <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Functions",
            "id": 79919,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Like before, a colon <code>:</code>, marks the beginning of the code block that belongs to the function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_user\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"17\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>:</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Functions",
            "id": 79922,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>To group code into the function, we indent it by two spaces. This function groups two related <code>print()</code> statements.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_user\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"54\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>print</code>, followed by <code>print</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Functions",
            "id": 79928,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>To run the code, we need to <strong>call</strong> the function. We do that by coding its name followed by parentheses, like <code>greet_user()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_user\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet_user()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"71\" endIndex=\"83\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Good morning Anna\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Welcome back\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>greet_user()</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
