          {
            "title": "Example: Function",
            "id": 79908,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code the <code>def</code> keyword to complete the function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"weather_update\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Weather update&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Sunny skies ahead&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"weather_update()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Weather update\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Sunny skies ahead\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>def</code>.</p></body></html>"
