            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Append another <code>print()</code> statement into the function's code block.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"launch\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;2&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;1&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Launch!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"launch()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"55\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"71\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Launch!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>print</code>, followed by <code>(\"Launch!\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
